{"en":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt32\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> The state of being held as <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/security\" title=\"security\">security</a> for a loan, or as a pledge.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"All our jewellery was in <b>pawn</b> by this stage."}],"examples":["All our jewellery was in <b>pawn</b> by this stage."]},{"definition":"An instance of pawning something."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt36\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> An item given as <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/security\" title=\"security\">security</a> on a loan, or as a pledge."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt40\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pawnshop\" title=\"pawnshop\">pawnshop</a>; <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pawnbroker\" title=\"pawnbroker\">pawnbroker</a>."}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Verb","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt101\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pledge\" title=\"pledge\">pledge</a>; to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/stake\" title=\"stake\">stake</a> or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/wager\" title=\"wager\">wager</a>."},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt102\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> To give as <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/security\" title=\"security\">security</a> on a <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/loan\" title=\"loan\">loan</a> of <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/money\" title=\"money\">money</a>; especially, to <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/deposit\" title=\"deposit\">deposit</a> (something) at a <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pawn_shop\" title=\"pawn shop\">pawn shop</a>."}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":""},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\"></span> The most numerous <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/chess\" title=\"chess\">chess</a> piece, or a similar piece in a similar game. In chess, each side starts with eight; moves are only <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/forward\" title=\"forward\">forward</a>, and <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/attack\" title=\"attack\">attacks</a> are only diagonally or <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/en_passant\" title=\"en passant\">en passant</a>."},{"definition":""},{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\"></span> A person being <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/manipulated\" title=\"manipulated\">manipulated</a> by another, being used to some end.","parsedExamples":[{"example":"Though a <b>pawn</b> of the gods, her departure is the precipitating cause of the Trojan War."}],"examples":["Though a <b>pawn</b> of the gods, her departure is the precipitating cause of the Trojan War."]}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt330\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Alternative form of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"en\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/paan#English\" title=\"paan\">paan</a></i></span></span>."}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"A <a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/gallery\" title=\"gallery\">gallery</a>.<!--Chambers 1908-->"}]},{"partOfSpeech":"Verb","language":"English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"usage-label-sense\" about=\"#mwt337\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\"></span> <span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt338\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">Alternative spelling of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"en\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pwn#English\" title=\"pwn\">pwn</a></i></span></span>."}]}],"other":[{"partOfSpeech":"Noun","language":"Middle English","definitions":[{"definition":"<span class=\"form-of-definition use-with-mention\" about=\"#mwt342\" typeof=\"mw:Transclusion\">alternative form of <span class=\"form-of-definition-link\"><i class=\"Latn mention\" lang=\"enm\"><a rel=\"mw:WikiLink\" href=\"/wiki/pown#Middle_English:_pawn\" title=\"pown\">pown</a></i> <span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">(</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">“</span><span class=\"mention-gloss\">pawn</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-double-quote\">”</span><span class=\"mention-gloss-paren annotation-paren\">)</span></span></span>"}]}]}